name: For Dimensional Chess
description: Outside hic et nunc I like to play chess. This was a recent checkmate I accomplished playing blitz. I thought it was a cool cm with the white king on g3 working in concert with the rook on h7 to check mate the king on h5. Minted ed/16, one for each piece on the board at the end of the game.  Hmu if you play chess - i’m on chess.com my name “tomburtonwood” i play blitz, daily etc.
